      • assertNoSamplesToRead

        private void assertNoSamplesToRead(Format endFormat)
        Asserts SampleQueue.read(com.google.android.exoplayer2.FormatHolder, com.google.android.exoplayer2.decoder.DecoderInputBuffer, boolean, boolean, long) is behaving correctly, given there are no samples to read and the last format to be written to the sample queue is endFormat.
        Parameters:
        endFormat - The last format to be written to the sample queue, or null of no format has been written.

      • assertReadEndOfStream

        private void assertReadEndOfStream(boolean formatRequired)
        Asserts SampleQueue.read(com.google.android.exoplayer2.FormatHolder, com.google.android.exoplayer2.decoder.DecoderInputBuffer, boolean, boolean, long) returns C.RESULT_BUFFER_READ and that the Buffer.isEndOfStream() is set.
        Parameters:

      • assertReadFormat

        private void assertReadFormat(boolean formatRequired,
                              Format format)
        Asserts SampleQueue.read(com.google.android.exoplayer2.FormatHolder, com.google.android.exoplayer2.decoder.DecoderInputBuffer, boolean, boolean, long) returns C.RESULT_FORMAT_READ and that the format holder is filled with a Format that equals format.
        Parameters:
        formatRequired - The value of formatRequired passed to readData.
        format - The expected format.

      • assertSampleRead

        private void assertSampleRead(long timeUs,
                              boolean isKeyframe,
                              byte[] sampleData,
                              int offset,
                              int length)
        Asserts SampleQueue.read(com.google.android.exoplayer2.FormatHolder, com.google.android.exoplayer2.decoder.DecoderInputBuffer, boolean, boolean, long) returns C.RESULT_BUFFER_READ and that the buffer is filled with the specified sample data.
        Parameters:
        timeUs - The expected buffer timestamp.
        isKeyframe - The expected keyframe flag.
        sampleData - An array containing the expected sample data.
        offset - The offset in sampleData of the expected sample data.
        length - The length of the expected sample data.
